org.knime.core.data.filestore.internal

Class WorkflowFileStoreHandlerRepository

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.data.filestore.internal.FileStoreHandlerRepository
      • org.knime.core.data.filestore.internal.WorkflowFileStoreHandlerRepository

  • public final class WorkflowFileStoreHandlerRepository
extends FileStoreHandlerRepository
    File store handler associated with a workflow. It's a map of store UUIDs to file store handlers. Each file store handler corresponds to a node.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, KNIME.com, Zurich, Switzerland
